web | url = http://www.esa.int/For_Media/Highlights/ESA_budget_2015 | title = ESA Budget for 2015 | work = esa.int | date = 16 January 2015}}</ref> Languages generally used are English and French. Additionally, official documents are also provided in German and documents regarding the [[Spacelab]] are also provided in Italian. If found appropriate, the agency may conduct its correspondence in any language of a member state.

